wikipedia_page.main: Joanna Gabrielle McGilchrist (born 27 August 1983) is an English rugby union player. She represented England at the 2010 Women's Rugby World Cup. She was also named in the squad to the 2014 Women's Rugby World Cup.McGilchrist is a physiotherapist.
